title: 820-3332 GPUVCORE_EN missing
message:
Hello everybody

I m working on liquid damaged 820-3332 , board is turning on, chime, usb mouse light is ok but no picture LCD. When checked voltage and heat GPU is cold and no GPU voltages, measured U8900 voltages and no GPUVCORE_EN. Its come from U9100 reballed and replaced also U9100 but nothing change . What can i do next step?

title: 820-3332 GPUVCORE_EN missing
message: The next step should have been the first step, resolder U8900.

title: 820-3332 GPUVCORE_EN missing
message: Thank you [USER="2"]dukefawks[/USER]  but resolder and replaced U8900 same issue

title: 820-3332 GPUVCORE_EN missing
message: GPUVCORE_EN only comes high when GPU recognized. It also does not stay high when all power good signals don't come on in time. Could be anything around the GPU area, corrosion under it. Maybe even a dead GPU too.
